The '''Chun family''' was socially prominent and very wealthy on [[Telos IV]] during the waning days of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]]. Its only known members were [[Vox Chun]], the corrupt [[Planet/Legends|planetary]] treasurer under the influence of the [[Dark Jedi/Legends|Dark Jedi]] [[Xanatos]], his oldest son [[Bruck Chun|Bruck]], a [[Star Wars: Jedi Apprentice|Jedi Apprentice]] whom Xanatos seduced to the [[Dark side of the Force/Legends|dark side]], and the younger son [[Kad Chun|Kad]].

